{
  "stem": "26359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what I remember, my grandmother-- I put it in the book even.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The grandmother went and she brought in a few religious books, and she kept them in one of the homes covered with her nice tablecloth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the same was with the church.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't allow churches also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the young Komsomols they climbed up, and they tore the crosses away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was the government against religion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both were denied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they-- somehow they trade with each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They mingled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember on the cold and winter days they used to come to the shtetl.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to stop by our-- my grandmother's house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were having tea with cookies, whatever the grandmother served them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- there was very good coexistence between the gentile people and the Jewish people-- only till the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they are very-- I used to see them Sunday in early in the morning going to church.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also the holidays.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used observe their holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of this changed when the Communist government took over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As they took over, they-- after the revolution.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the '20s, everything changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seven years of school I went to a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish language was the main subject.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all said once a week or twice week Ukrainian language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the same as in the schools here-- arithmetic, geography, and history and everything were taught there by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then after seven years, I went to a bigger city, [UKRAINIAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wanted to be a school teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the government--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they helped me a lot with education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They provided books for me for free, and also  I had the dormitories to share with the other girls a room.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
